-- Adviser Basu Expects Sharp Decline in India's Inflation in Next Few Weeks
-- B y   T u s h a r   D h a r a
-- 2010-11-16T05:22:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/adviser-basu-expects-sharp-decline-in-india-s-inflation-in-next-few-weeks.html
Kaushik Basu, chief economic adviser
in the Ministry of Finance, said he expects a “sharp decline”
in the country’s inflation rate in the next few weeks. Basu was
talking to reporters in New Delhi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
